header.gameNote: NCAA Women's Championship pres. by Capital One - Final Four

videos.headline: Hull drains a 3 in defender's face
videos.description: Lexie Hull pulls up and poses as she nails a 3-pointer right in the face of the defense to give Stanford a 22-17 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Hull drains a 3 in defender's face) 2021/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: South Carolina's Boston comes up with big block
videos.description: Aliyah Boston comes up huge for South Carolina shutting down the Stanford layup attempt for her third block of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (South Carolina's Boston comes up with big block) 2021/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cooke poses as she drains another 3
videos.description: Zia Cooke poses as she drains her fourth 3-pointer of the game for South Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Cooke poses as she drains another 3) 2021/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jones knocks down another big 3 for Stanford
videos.description: Haley Jones pulls up to confidently knock down a 3-pointer as Stanford increases their lead to 48-45.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Jones knocks down another big 3 for Stanford) 2021/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brink lets out a yell after emphatic block
videos.description: Cameron Brink lets out a yell after she pursues the basketball and comes up with a massive block for Stanford.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Brink lets out a yell after emphatic block) 2021/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Missed kick ball call ends in Stanford fast-break bucket
videos.description: Referees miss a blatant kick ball by Stanford and it ends up gifting Cameron Brink with a fast-break layup late in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Missed kick ball call ends in Stanford fast break bucket) 2021/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Henderson knocks down clutch 3 for South Carolina
videos.description: South Carolina takes a late 65-64 lead over Stanford as Destanni Henderson knocks down a clutch 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Henderson knocks down clutch 3 for South Carolina) 2021/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jones hits off-balance shot to give Stanford the lead
videos.description: Haley Jones comes up big for Stanford hitting an off-balance shot to give Stanford a one-point lead with only 32 seconds remaining.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Jones hits off-balance shot to give Stanford the lead) 2021/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stanford defeats South Carolina in thrilling ending
videos.description: Aliyah Boston misses the game-winning putback shot, and Stanford escapes with a 66-65 win to advance to the national championship.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Stanford defeats South Carolina in thrilling ending) 2021/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stanford escapes with win in wild final minute to advance to national championship
videos.description: Stanford and South Carolina battle in the final minute, as the Gamecocks miss out on a buzzer-beating winner by inches.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Highlight (Stanford escapes with win in wild final minute to advance to national championship) 2021/04/02 ESHEET SOTFULL
